1
00:00:29,830 --> 00:00:30,830
Ying Wujiu.

2
00:00:30,830 --> 00:00:32,800
You are a mutilated eunuch.

3
00:00:32,830 --> 00:00:34,690
Yet you dare to covet the Empress!

4
00:00:35,130 --> 00:00:37,800
I merely mentioned to His Majesty

5
00:00:38,200 --> 00:00:40,460
your filthy thoughts about the Empress.

6
00:00:40,630 --> 00:00:41,960
The Emperor's jealousy

7
00:00:42,130 --> 00:00:46,130
is enough to have you, the Director of the Eastern Depot, skinned alive.

8
00:00:48,230 --> 00:00:49,230
Old dog Yu.

9
00:00:50,230 --> 00:00:51,760
What do you know?

10
00:01:00,700 --> 00:01:02,560
May Your Highness

11
00:01:02,560 --> 00:01:03,830
have a smooth life.

12
00:01:09,630 --> 00:01:10,500
Ying Wujiu,

13
00:01:11,300 --> 00:01:13,230
you planned for me your whole life,

14
00:01:13,860 --> 00:01:16,460
only to end up dying with a pierced heart.

15
00:01:17,830 --> 00:01:18,930
In the next life,

16
00:01:19,760 --> 00:01:22,660
let me protect you.

17
00:01:25,930 --> 00:01:28,060
The Qu family has been dead for 3 years.

18
00:01:28,430 --> 00:01:31,760
The Prime Minister kept you in the water dungeon for 3 whole years.

19
00:01:31,760 --> 00:01:35,289
He used the world's rarest medicines to cultivate your beauty.

20
00:01:35,729 --> 00:01:38,030
He kept your pure virgin body

21
00:01:38,360 --> 00:01:41,300
just so you could climb into the Emperor's bed.

22
00:01:43,630 --> 00:01:45,430
If you still keep this dead face,

23
00:01:46,100 --> 00:01:48,360
your younger brother exiled in Ningguta

24
00:01:48,660 --> 00:01:50,560
will be beheaded tomorrow.

25
00:01:53,060 --> 00:01:53,900
I understand.

26
00:01:54,300 --> 00:01:56,100
I belong to the Yu family in life,

27
00:01:56,130 --> 00:01:57,759
and a ghost of the Yu family in death.

28
00:01:57,759 --> 00:01:59,630
Stop acting pitiful.

29
00:02:03,400 --> 00:02:05,460
Go clean the chamber pots in the yard.

30
00:02:10,600 --> 00:02:12,260
Useless wench.

31
00:02:12,660 --> 00:02:14,730
You can't even clean a pot properly.

32
00:02:20,900 --> 00:02:21,900
I'm not dead.

33
00:02:22,860 --> 00:02:25,260
No. I have been reborn.

34
00:02:26,060 --> 00:02:27,160
Let me ask you.

35
00:02:27,460 --> 00:02:29,060
What is the date today?

36
00:02:30,960 --> 00:02:31,360
Wu...

37
00:02:31,560 --> 00:02:32,230
Wuxu Year,

38
00:02:32,530 --> 00:02:34,060
the 3rd day of the 3rd month.

39
00:02:35,100 --> 00:02:38,060
Ying Wujiu, wait for me. Reborn in this life,

40
00:02:38,060 --> 00:02:41,390
I will never let you become a mutilated cripple for me again.

41
00:02:41,829 --> 00:02:43,530
Even if I have to risk my life,

42
00:02:43,760 --> 00:02:45,760
I will block that strike.

43
00:02:50,930 --> 00:02:52,260
No.

44
00:02:52,260 --> 00:02:54,160
Why isn't Ying Wujiu's name here?

45
00:02:54,160 --> 00:02:56,160
It was clearly today in my past life.

46
00:02:57,000 --> 00:02:58,460
Where exactly are you?

47
00:02:59,300 --> 00:03:00,700
Where did this lowly servant come from?

48
00:03:00,700 --> 00:03:04,500
How dare you trespass into the castration room of the Eastern Depot?

49
00:03:05,260 --> 00:03:07,860
Which servant is yelling?

50
00:03:20,630 --> 00:03:23,630
I pay my respects to the Director of the Eastern Depot.

51
00:03:26,329 --> 00:03:28,060
Director of the Eastern Depot?

52
00:03:31,760 --> 00:03:33,890
The timeline has completely changed.

53
00:03:34,329 --> 00:03:37,000
You actually wore the python robe 3 years early.

54
00:03:37,700 --> 00:03:40,829
Could it be that you became a mutilated cripple long ago?

55
00:03:40,829 --> 00:03:42,130
Jingzhi.

56
00:03:42,630 --> 00:03:44,260
I turned the capital upside down

57
00:03:44,260 --> 00:03:45,920
and looked for you for 3 years.

58
00:03:46,200 --> 00:03:47,730
So that old fool Yu Henian

59
00:03:47,800 --> 00:03:49,930
actually hid you in a water dungeon.

60
00:03:50,400 --> 00:03:51,530
You've suffered.

61
00:03:53,130 --> 00:03:54,329
Lord Thousand Years.

62
00:03:54,329 --> 00:03:57,030
This servant bumped into you suspiciously.

63
00:03:57,030 --> 00:03:58,600
I will finish her off.

64
00:04:05,830 --> 00:04:07,460
Spare my life, Lord Thousand Years!

65
00:04:07,460 --> 00:04:08,930
My rules.

66
00:04:09,600 --> 00:04:11,200
Don't make me repeat myself.

67
00:04:12,030 --> 00:04:12,960
Clean it up.

68
00:04:13,960 --> 00:04:14,700
Yes.

69
00:04:21,160 --> 00:04:23,500
I don't care which palace you are from.

70
00:04:24,100 --> 00:04:26,960
If you dare to look at me with that kind of look again,

71
00:04:27,300 --> 00:04:29,760
I will personally gouge your eyes out.

72
00:04:29,760 --> 00:04:30,330
Get out!

73
00:04:36,200 --> 00:04:38,400
The Yu family's spies are watching her.

74
00:04:38,430 --> 00:04:41,290
She is now a dead pawn used by the Yu family to test me.

75
00:04:41,330 --> 00:04:42,400
Jingzhi,

76
00:04:42,400 --> 00:04:44,530
if I show even a hint of heartache right now,

77
00:04:44,530 --> 00:04:47,060
you will die without a burial place tomorrow.

78
00:04:47,159 --> 00:04:48,159
Hate me.

79
00:04:48,460 --> 00:04:50,800
I must be the most ruthless demon.

80
00:04:51,100 --> 00:04:51,860
Ying Wujiu.

81
00:04:52,360 --> 00:04:53,560
Don't try to fool me.

82
00:04:53,960 --> 00:04:56,230
The look in your eyes when you killed to protect me

83
00:04:56,230 --> 00:04:58,400
was exactly the same as in our past life.

84
00:04:58,400 --> 00:04:59,360
For my sake,

85
00:04:59,430 --> 00:05:02,160
you put on this hellish python robe three years early.

86
00:05:02,160 --> 00:05:04,500
If you become a demon in this life,

87
00:05:04,500 --> 00:05:06,560
I will join you in eternal damnation.

88
00:05:24,800 --> 00:05:25,600
Jingzhi.
